snippet.title: Tales Of Destiny Trailer 1998
snippet.description:
Tales Of Destiny Trailer 1998

Official Content From Namco

Stan, a boy stowed away in a flying dragon ship, stumbles on a sentient sword that thinks and speaks for itself. Choose from 6 swords that hold the key to saving the land from doom.
Platforms: Sony PlayStation

Sony PlayStation
